name: Roots °_°
description:
Dear Mother Earth,

I am sorry for the way I have treated you. I have not been mindful of how my actions impact you. I have abused your resources and failed to appreciate your beauty. I pledge to do better from now on. I will be more mindful of how my choices impact you, and I will work to protect and preserve you. Thank you for giving me another chance. I promise to make the most of it.

Sincerely,

Your Child
